516
00:30:23,009 --> 00:30:26,207
And no matter what you hear,
tell them I'm doing okay.

517
00:30:27,047 --> 00:30:28,006
You mean, you want me to lie?

518
00:30:29,845 --> 00:30:32,484
It's a good lie, Father.
