574
00:36:12,354 --> 00:36:13,633
No, it don't go for you.

575
00:36:14,113 --> 00:36:18,311
You go back to your room.
You're through with your lunch. Go on.

576
00:36:20,110 --> 00:36:22,908
You and me...we're gonna finish
this sometime real soon.

577
00:36:23,388 --> 00:36:24,308
Maybe at dinner.

578
00:36:24,508 --> 00:36:28,706
So...you Hell's Kitchen
boys get any lunch?

579
00:36:31,264 --> 00:36:32,344
I got to smell it.

580
00:36:33,783 --> 00:36:35,542
You got to smell it...

581
00:36:38,940 --> 00:36:39,700
That's good.

582
00:36:41,219 --> 00:36:42,059
Where you going?

583
00:36:42,938 --> 00:36:44,018
You said to get lunch.

584
00:36:44,937 --> 00:36:47,896
You boys don't need to get back
in line to get lunch 'cause...

585
00:36:48,056 --> 00:36:50,295
...there's plenty to eat right
where you're standing.

586
00:36:51,214 --> 00:36:52,374
You could smell it.

587
00:36:57,891 --> 00:36:58,930
I'm not hungry.

588
00:37:00,010 --> 00:37:02,089
Well, I don't give a fuck
if you're hungry or not.

589
00:37:02,888 --> 00:37:04,808
You eat...because I'm
telling you to eat.

590
00:37:09,565 --> 00:37:10,845
I'm still not hungry.

591
00:37:16,802 --> 00:37:18,681
I'll tell you when
you're hungry or not.

592
00:37:18,841 --> 00:37:19,680
Now, eat.

593
00:37:22,759 --> 00:37:25,157
Excuse me? What the
fuck are you looking at?

594
00:37:25,717 --> 00:37:29,395
Get the fuck down on your knees
now and finish your goddam lunch!

595
00:37:30,914 --> 00:37:34,233
Come on now, eat! Don't think you
got all fucking day, here! Eat!

596
00:37:34,633 --> 00:37:38,271
You've got some mashed potatoes...
come on, suck up some of that jello.

597
00:37:38,431 --> 00:37:42,109
Come on now, you fucking assholes, eat!
Don't be thinking you got all day.

598
00:37:42,269 --> 00:37:43,988
Hurry up. Come on, now, let's go.

599
00:37:45,147 --> 00:37:49,625
